{"pid":"71d350b84e5c72a53027e805dadb0371ede2c5bb","tid":1367103,"uid":1852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:09:19.000Z","msg":"想辭職，好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3006dddd7063bc19502d2d0786eacb112adf71d","tid":1367103,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71d350b84e5c72a53027e805dadb0371ede2c5bb","tid":1367103,"uid":1852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:09:19.000Z","msg":"想辭職，好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:50:31.000Z","msg":"咩事"},{"pid":"d8bbb0306916bf096dcb2156b89a64490e55b28f","tid":1367103,"uid":1852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3006dddd7063bc19502d2d0786eacb112adf71d","tid":1367103,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71d350b84e5c72a53027e805dadb0371ede2c5bb","tid":1367103,"uid":1852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:09:19.000Z","msg":"想辭職，好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:50:31.000Z","msg":"咩事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:58:43.000Z","msg":"一黎呢排返工不在狀態，之後我老闆走黎話我啦，其實呢個只係導火線<br />\n<br />\n佢話我果樣野其實本身唔係我職責黎，我只係一路幫佢頂住做埋佢<br />\n<br />\n同埋我本身有透露我根本唔想做呢個職責，而佢地係知.....<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知係生意差&quot;借啲意&quot;搵野黎講，定係點<br />\n<br />\n我知自己唔叫做得好好，但自問可以做嘅都盡力做，之前都叫幫佢地度過左d 障礙，唉，好撚灰<br />\n<br />\n諗住星期一裸辭<br />\n<br />\n其實香港咁樣，你要我笑我真係笑唔出，我都有反思自己係咪為佢地帶黎乜野不便, 呢段期間我諗我試過請4-5日假啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31926aac895d36c03fe1e587c07481c3193a73fe","tid":1367103,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8bbb0306916bf096dcb2156b89a64490e55b28f","tid":1367103,"uid":1852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3006dddd7063bc19502d2d0786eacb112adf71d","tid":1367103,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71d350b84e5c72a5302